<h2 id="ftp">FTP</h2>
<p>FTP:File Transfer Protocol<br>
TFTP:Trivial File Transfer Protocol,简单文件传输协议</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0vn759"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0vn759.png" alt="0vn759.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0vuOij"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0vuOij.png" alt="0vuOij.png" loading="lazy"></a><br>
主动:建立连接后,S主动告诉C是20端口发送数据<br>
被动:建立连接后,C问S,S告诉一个端口号<br>
<a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0vKPwF"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0vKPwF.png" alt="0vKPwF.png" loading="lazy"></a></p>
<h2 id="电子邮件">电子邮件</h2>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v1GE8"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v1GE8.png" alt="0v1GE8.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v1p9J"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v1p9J.png" alt="0v1p9J.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v1ags"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v1ags.png" alt="0v1ags.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<h3 id="smtpsimple-mail-transfer-protocol">SMTP:Simple Mail Transfer Protocol</h3>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v3rQA"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v3rQA.png" alt="0v3rQA.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>** 注意**<br>
端口587只应用于提交（即，邮件客户端到邮件服务器）<br>
端口25只应用于中继（即，邮件服务器到邮件服务器通信</p>
</blockquote>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v3IQs"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v3IQs.png" alt="0v3IQs.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<h3 id="pop3post-office-protocol">POP3:Post Office Protocol</h3>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v8SyR"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v8SyR.png" alt="0v8SyR.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<h3 id="imapinternet-message-access-protocol因特网报文存取协议">IMAP:Internet Message Access Protocol(因特网报文存取协议)</h3>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v8eld"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v8eld.png" alt="0v8eld.png" loading="lazy"></a></figure>
<h3 id="基于万维网的电子邮件">基于万维网的电子邮件</h3>
<p><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/0v8amq"><img src="https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/10/19/0v8amq.png" alt="0v8amq.png" loading="lazy"></a><br>
